---
title: Creamy Rigatoni With Pork Sausage plus Philadelphia Cream Cheese, Broccoli, Lemon & Parmesan
description: Pasta is a mealtime savior that can be made and on the table before your hanger sets in. This easy rigatoni dish is ready in just 20 minutes. Juicy Italian pork sausage combines with short, sturdy pasta tubes in a quick and creamy sauce. Toss in some crisp-tender steamed broccoli and sprinkle on Parm for an all-in-one meal that’s here for the rescue!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-rigatoni-with-pork-sausage-9f5c9aca.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/creamy-rigatoni-with-pork-sausage-61d4c2e38e0da9642154d49b-7f0b1d0c.pdf
